<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٩٨٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">غُنْدَرٌ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3120">عُبَادَةَ بْنِ الصَّامِتِ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«رُؤْيَا الْمُؤْمِنِ جُزْءٌ مِنْ سِتَّةٍ وَأَرْبَعِينَ جُزْءًا مِنَ النُّبُوَّةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>